Class User

java.lang.Object
  org.pmedv.pojos.User
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<User>

This class represents a user of this cms, which can be assigned to multiple groups Any user can have one or more avatars (in order to switch between multiple avatars)

Author:
Matthias Pueski
